@startuml DocCheck_UseCase
title DocCheck Module - Use Case Diagram

left to right direction

actor Seller as S
actor System as SYS

rectangle DocCheck {
  usecase "Access DocCheck Tool" as UC1
  usecase "Answer Assessment Questions" as UC2
  usecase "Evaluate Document Requirements" as UC3
  usecase "View Result & Recommendations" as UC4
  usecase "Capture Email" as UC5
  usecase "Recommend Service Tier" as UC6
  usecase "Display Risk Flags" as UC7
  usecase "Persist Session" as UC8
}

S --> UC1
UC1 --> UC2
UC2 --> UC3
UC3 --> UC5
UC5 --> UC4
UC3 --> UC6
UC3 --> UC7
UC3 --> UC8

SYS --> UC3
SYS --> UC6

note right of UC2
  8 questions
  branching logic
  < 90 seconds
end note

note right of UC4
  Document checklist
  Tier recommendation
  Price estimate
  Timeline
end note

note right of UC8
  24-hour browser
  session storage
end note

@enduml
